  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Application scenarios",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti airMAX Rocket Prism 5AC Gen2 (RP-5AC-Gen2) is tailored for a broad spectrum of application scenarios, excelling in delivering high-speed, reliable wireless connectivity across vast distances. In urban environments, its cutting-edge airPrism technology ensures that the device stands out by mitigating interference from other signals, which is a common challenge in densely populated areas. This makes it an ideal solution for ISPs and network operators looking to provide high-quality, uninterrupted internet service to customers in residential and commercial zones. The device's ability to support high-throughput, low-latency connections makes it perfect for applications requiring robust bandwidth, such as video streaming, VoIP, and online gaming. Furthermore, its dedicated management Wi-Fi radio simplifies setup and ongoing network adjustments, making it a breeze for network administrators to maintain optimal performance."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Performance and Hardware",
      "text": "In rural or remote areas, the Rocket Prism 5AC Gen2's capabilities are equally valuable. Its long-range connectivity, facilitated by the 5 GHz frequency band and high-gain antenna compatibility, offers a lifeline for communities and businesses located far from traditional wired internet infrastructures. For applications like remote surveillance, environmental monitoring, and providing internet access to distant research stations or agricultural sites, the RP-5AC-Gen2 provides a reliable, high-performance link. The device's rugged, weather-resistant design ensures consistent operation in diverse environmental conditions, from scorching deserts to freezing mountaintops, offering a versatile solution for connecting the unconnected and bridging digital divides across varied landscapes."
    }
  ],
